# BX Finance Banking Demo — Windsurf Project Rules

## Project Overview

Full-stack banking demo built on PingOne. Three packages:

| Package | Language | Role |
|---|---|---|
| `banking_api_server` | JavaScript (CJS, Node 18+) | BFF — Express API server, holds all tokens server-side |
| `banking_api_ui` | JavaScript + JSX (React 18, CRA) | SPA — session cookies only, never raw tokens |
| `banking_mcp_server` | TypeScript (strict, Node 18+) | MCP WebSocket server — NOT on Vercel |

Deployed on Vercel (api + UI). MCP server deployed separately on Railway/Render/Fly.io.

